{{Expand French|Brevet d'État d'éducateur sportif|date=July 2012|topic = sport}}
'''Brevet d'Etat d'éducateur sportif'''" (BEES) (''State Certified Sports Instructor'') is a [[France|French]] government certificate for [[coach (sports)|sport coaches]]. Only holders of this certificate may be paid for sports coaching.
==See also== *[[Minister of Youth Affairs and Sports (France)]]
==External links== * [https://web.archive.org/web/20071017225821/http://www.jeunesse-sports.gouv.fr/ Ministère de la Jeunesse et des Sports] * [https://web.archive.org/web/20071012021707/http://www.jeunesse-sports.gouv.fr/emploi-formations_4/les-formations-diplomes-professionnels-sport-animation_103/les-formations-diplomes-professionnels-bees-dedpad-defa-beatep-bapaat-bpjeps_415/bees-brevet-etat-educateur-sportif_321.html Description of the BEES in French, Sport's Ministry website] * [https://web.archive.org/web/20071016054751/http://www.ipac-france.com/Formations/BEES.php IPAC]
