'''Daniele Di Spigino''' (born 19 September 1974) is an Italian [[Shooting sports|sport shooter]].

He participated at the [[2018 ISSF World Shooting Championships]], winning a medal.<ref>[https://www.issf-sports.org/media/resultspdf/2018/1750/I100000TA0809180830.1.DT150.0.001.pdf Team double trap results]</ref>

